These programs use the library that is in the /library directory of the
GitHub repository. To use this library you should perform the following
steps:

pi@ERPi ~ $ cd ~/exploringrpi/library/build
pi@ERPi ~/exploringrpi/library/build $ cmake ..
pi@ERPi ~/exploringrpi/library/build $ make
pi@ERPi ~/exploringrpi/library/build $ sudo make install
pi@ERPi ~/exploringrpi/library/build $ cd ~/exploringrpi/chp08/spi/spiADXL345_cpp
pi@ERPi ~/exploringrpi/chp08/spi/spiADXL345_cpp $ ./build
